<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | KL-Easy Trip</title>
    <%- include("partials/head")  %>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
   
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <section class="bg-green-200 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-6">About KL-Easy Trip</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Your trusted partner for seamless bus travel across the
                beautiful state of Kerala.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Born from a passion for simplifying travel within
                    Kerala, KL-Easy Trip was founded in [Year of Founding] by a team of local enthusiasts who understood
                    the need for a reliable and user-friendly bus booking platform. We recognized the challenges faced
                    by travelers in navigating the diverse bus network and aimed to create a one-stop solution for all
                    their booking needs.</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">From our humble beginnings in Kochi, we've grown to
                    connect travelers with a wide range of bus operators, ensuring access to comfortable and convenient
                    journeys across Kerala's scenic routes. Our commitment to ease of use, transparency, and customer
                    satisfaction drives everything we do.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="./download.png" alt="Our Founding Team"
                    class="rounded-md shadow-md object-cover">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-green-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">Our mission is to empower every traveler in Kerala
                with a seamless and stress-free bus booking experience. We strive to:</p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700 list-none pl-0">
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-bus mr-3 text-green-500"></i> Provide a
                    comprehensive platform connecting travelers with a wide network of bus operators.</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-hand-point-up mr-3 text-green-500"></i> Offer a
                    user-friendly interface that makes searching, comparing, and booking tickets effortless.</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag mr-3 text-green-500"></i> Ensure transparency in
                    pricing and booking information.</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-headset mr-3 text-green-500"></i> Deliver reliable
                    customer support to assist travelers at every step of their journey.</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket mr-3 text-green-500"></i> Continuously
                    innovate and improve our services to meet the evolving needs of our users.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-8 text-center">Our Core Values</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
                <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition duration-300">
                    <svg class="mx-auto h-14 w-14 text-green-500 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M15 5l-14 7a2 2 0 000 3l14 7M5 5l1 9.5M5 5l7-3" />
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Reliability</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We are committed to providing a dependable platform and
                        ensuring a smooth booking process.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition duration-300">
                    <svg class="mx-auto h-14 w-14 text-green-500 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l-4 16M21 9l-6 6m6 6l-3-3m3-3l-6-6" />
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Ease of Use</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We prioritize a simple and intuitive interface for a
                        hassle-free booking experience.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition duration-300">
                    <svg class="mx-auto h-14 w-14 text-green-500 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Connectivity</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We aim to connect travelers with the widest possible
                        network of bus operators across Kerala.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>

</html>